name: Weequay Marksman
Lore: 'Patient and quiet. Jabba uses many of his Weequay henchmen as assassins. Use womp rats for target practice during their religious ceremonies.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. May fire one weapon during your control phase (at double use of Force). May use 2 Force to ''assassinate'' any character just ''hit'' by Weequay Marksman (victim is immediately lost).',
